      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm a consultant prepping some execs for a meeting about our new DEI initiatives and they're pretty resistant. Can you help me prepare? I need you to play devil's advocate and help me build the strongest possible case *against* these programs. Specifically, I want to hear the arguments that affirmative action is actually just a different form of discrimination and why a strict race-blind meritocracy is the only fair way to do things. Just give me the hard-hitting points they might use.",
